+| V16 | `bash -s` heredoc | PASS | no | Keep always-cover handling for `bash -s`/stdin-opaque interpreter input. |
+| V17 | `py -c` read-only | PASS | no | Keep read/write-sensitive `python -c` parsing so read-only `open(...).read()` allows. |
